00:00:32.749 --> 00:00:37.930
Mattel created the original Skipper doll in
1964, in response to requests of Barbie fans

00:00:37.930 --> 00:00:40.370
wanting Barbie to have children of her own.

00:00:40.370 --> 00:00:45.080
Given how Skipper eventually turned out, one
