00:00:56.830 --> 00:01:01.910
Apparently not wanting to create “Knocked
Up Barbie”, Mattel created Skipper Roberts,

00:01:01.910 --> 00:01:03.350
Barbie’s younger sister.

00:01:03.350 --> 00:01:08.000
The idea was that Barbie would babysit Skipper,
who in turn, would bring out all the maternal

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.310
